        {
          "field_name": "tiered_rate_flag",
          "candidate_value": "true",
          "evidence_chunk_id": "chunk-33aa0cfca2614b1e",
          "evidence_text_excerpt": "is determined\nYour HISA interest rate is determined by your Total Relationship\u00a0Balance 1 , which is\u00a0the combined daily closing balance\u00a0in your eligible chequing , savings ,\u00a0and investment accounts.\n$10,000 minimum Total Relationship Balance 1 required\u00a0to earn interest 3\nGet the promo rate for 3 months, on top of our regular tiered interest rates 2 when you keep a Total Relationship Balance 1 of at least $10,000.",
          "source_document_id": "src-scotia-html-d938019b2d45b48a",
