          "evidence_chunk_id": "chunk-446451241d4e43d6",
          "evidence_text_excerpt": "Eligible investment accounts\nThe funds in these investment accounts count towards your\u00a0Total\u00a0Relationship\u00a0Balance 1 :\nTax-Free Savings Account (TFSA)\nRegistered Education Savings Plan (RESP) \u2013 Individual and Family\nFirst Home Savings Account (FHSA)\nRegistered Disability Savings Plan\u00a0(RDSP)\nRegistered Retirement Savings Plan (RRSP)\nRegistered Retirement Income Fund\nLocked-In Retirement Income Fund\nPrescribed Retirement Income Fund\nRestricted Locked-in Savings Plan\nLocked-In Retirement Savings Plan\nSpousal Reg Retirement Savings Plan\nRestricted Life Income Fund\nLocked-In Retirement Account\nLife Income Fund\nSpousal Reg Retirement Income Fund\nNon-Registered Savings \u2013 Personal\nFunds in\u00a0ScotiaMcLeod\u00a0or\u00a0iTRADE \u00ae accounts, or in investment accounts that aren\u2019t listed, won\u2019t count towards your Total Relationship Balance 1 .",
          "source_document_id": "src-scotia-html-d938019b2d45b48a",
